1) Create a dynamic project
2) Add All Jar files-- Web-inf/lib folder
3) Create 3 packages-- com.springcrud.controller, com.springcrud.beans, com.springcrud.Dao
4) Create a folder JSP in web-inf
5) create index.jsp in Webcontent folder
6) create spring-servlet.xml in web-inf

1) Configuration (XML)
	i) in web.xml-- configure welcome page & DispatcherServlet
	ii) in spring-servlet.xml- Configure viewresolver, datasource, jdbctemplate, DAO class
	ii
	JDBCTemplate is providing us all predefined methods to do CRUD operations
2) Bean- create Employee.java (Class)
3) DAO- create EmmployeeDaO.java (Class), EmployeeMapper(Class)
4)controller -- 
	